cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.CY

This paper deals with privacy and security issues related to mobile devices, specifically location inference and sensor side-channel attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the design and implementation of a system, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.SE (Software Engineering). The system involves the use of synthetic location trajectories, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
